cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.HC, cs.IR, cs.LG 

The paper deals with video analysis and human cognition, which are both related to computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM). The concept of memorability is also related to human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the development of a prediction model involves machine learning (cs.LG).
